  "text": [
    "Two women with",
    "the same claim",
    "came to the feet of",
    "the wise king. Two women,",
    "but only one baby.",
    "The king knew",
    "someone was lying.",
    "What he said was",
    "Let the child be",
    "cut in half; that way",
    "no one will go",
    "empty-handed. He",
    "drew his sword.",
    "Then, of the two",
    "women, one",
    "renounced her share:",
    "this was",
    "the sign, the lesson.",
    "Suppose",
    "you saw your mother",
    "torn between two daughters:",
    "what could you do",
    "to save her but be",
    "willing to destroy",
    "yourself\u2014she would know",
    "who was the rightful child,",
    "the one who couldn\u2019t bear",
    "to divide the mother."
  ],
  "title": "A Fable",
